      Jodie Nierintz, Phone 978-491-9290, <url href="mailto:jnierintz@framingham.edu">jnierintz@framingham.edu</url>.
    </p>
  </paragraphs>
  <paragraphs>
    <title>Office Hours</title>
    <p>
      Please email to set up an appt for office hours.
    </p>
  </paragraphs>
